cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.CE, cs.IT

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on cellular networks and their energy consumption. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is also likely as the paper proposes an optimization problem and solution. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with the control of energy systems in base stations. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is relevant as the paper deals with the cost optimization of deploying green energy systems. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with the QoS requirements of cellular networks.
